Mutua is in form three. He joined St. Mathews Sesinia in 2009. He comes from a family of five and the father is the only breadwinner. The father is just a hawker whose income is unstabble. Mutua is a hardworking boy but due to financial difficulties, he at times performs poorly but if assisted can do very well. He treks to and from school to his house which is five kilometers away from school.
